OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FSome bright
OL,6,Fspells possible at first in the
OL,7,Fevening but a band of cloud and rain
OL,8,Fsoon spreads northeast. This becomes
OL,9,Fheavy at times before clearing to
OL,10,Fshowers towards morning.
OL,11,
OL,12,CFriday:FA cloudy start with scattered
OL,13,Fshowers. The showers will decrease as
OL,14,Fbright or sunny spells increase from
OL,15,Flate morning.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
