OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FCloud
OL,6,Fand rain soon push northeast Saturday,
OL,7,Fdrier and clearer later. Rain becomes
OL,8,Fheavy Sunday before clearing to a few
OL,9,Fshowers early Monday, becoming drier,
OL,10,Fbrighter in the afternoon.
